# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Model and gallery artifacts. These never ship in the open repo.
#
# Two layers on purpose. The extension lists catch a stray artifact anywhere
# in the tree. The asset-directory rules at the bottom deny by default, so a
# file with a name nobody predicted is still ignored.
#
# The rules here used to name master_index.bin / master_index_ids.txt
# explicitly. Those are v2-era names; when the v3 files landed under new
# names the rules silently covered nothing. Do not go back to listing files
# one at a time -- widen the pattern instead.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Trained weights and converted graphs
*.tflite
*.onnx
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.safetensors
*.pb
*.gguf
*.engine
*.plan
*.dlc
*.mlmodel
*.mlpackage/
*.mlmodelc/
*.param
*.ncnn
*.ort
*.lite
*.tfl
*.weights
*.h5

# Embedding galleries, indexes, and their id/family sidecars
*.bin
*.npy
*.npz
*.pkl
master_index*
printlens_*

# Bundled asset directories: deny by default, then allow the card catalog.
#
# Deny-by-default is the point. Naming individual model files here is what
# rotted last time -- the rules listed master_index.bin, the v3 files landed
# under new names, and nothing caught them. Anything dropped in these
# directories is ignored unless it appears on a "!" line below.
#
# cards.db is public card data derived from TCGdex and is tracked on purpose.
# Note it is ~37MB and changes wholesale on every rebuild (VACUUM repacks the
# file), so each committed update adds roughly that much to history and git
# cannot delta it.
composeApp/src/androidMain/assets/*
!composeApp/src/androidMain/assets/cards.db
composeApp/src/debug/assets/*
iosApp/iosApp/BundledAssets/*
!iosApp/iosApp/BundledAssets/cards.db
**/assets/metadata.yaml

# Signing material and environment files
.env
.env.*
.envrc
*.env
key.properties
google-services.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
*.jks
*.keystore
*.p12
*.pem
*.key
*.cer
*.crt
*.der
*.mobileprovision
*.provisionprofile

# Miscellaneous generated files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
tmp_frame*.png
